# Flutter Conventions

## Folder structure (feature-first)
```
lib/
  main_standard.dart       # entry: injects OneSignalNotificationService
  main_fdroid.dart         # entry: injects UnifiedPushNotificationService
  main_huawei.dart         # entry: injects HuaweiNotificationService
  src/
    app.dart               # MaterialApp.router — theme + router wired here
    features/
      programmes/
        data/              # ProgrammesRepository, ProgrammesRemoteDataSource
        domain/            # Programme model, ProgrammeType enum, ProgrammeStatus enum
        presentation/
          programmes_list_screen.dart
          programme_detail_screen.dart
          programmes_filter_sheet.dart
          providers/       # programmes_provider.dart, filter_provider.dart
      auth/
        data/              # AuthRepository
        presentation/
          login_screen.dart
          register_screen.dart
          providers/       # auth_provider.dart
      saved/
        data/              # SavedRepository
        presentation/
          saved_screen.dart
          providers/       # saved_provider.dart
      notifications/
        presentation/
          providers/       # notification_provider.dart
      admin/
        presentation/
          review_queue_screen.dart
          providers/       # review_queue_provider.dart
      submit/
        presentation/
          submit_programme_screen.dart
    core/
      notifications/
        notification_service.dart               # abstract interface
        onesignal_notification_service.dart
        unified_push_notification_service.dart
        huawei_notification_service.dart
      router/
        app_router.dart                         # all routes here
        app_routes.dart                         # route name constants
      supabase/
        supabase_init.dart                      # Supabase.initialize()
        database_types.dart                     # generated: supabase gen types dart
      theme/
        app_theme.dart                          # MaterialTheme class
      utils/
        date_utils.dart
        constants.dart
```

## Riverpod rules
- Use `@riverpod` annotation + `riverpod_generator`. Run `dart run build_runner watch` during dev.
- **`AsyncNotifier<T>`** — any provider that performs async work (Supabase queries, etc.)
- **`Notifier<T>`** — sync state (filter state, UI toggles, tab index)
- Never use `StateProvider` for anything with more than one field.
- Providers live in `features/<feature>/presentation/providers/`.
- Widgets never call Supabase directly. Flow: widget → provider → repository → Supabase.
- Always expose `AsyncValue<T>` from async providers. Widgets consume `.when(data:, loading:, error:)`.

## go_router rules
- All routes defined in `lib/src/core/router/app_router.dart`. No `Navigator.push` anywhere.
- Route name constants in `AppRoutes` class in `app_routes.dart`.
- Auth guard in router's `redirect` callback — never in a screen's `initState` or `build`.
- Use `context.go()` for replacing stack, `context.push()` for pushing. Never `Navigator.*`.

## NotificationService pattern
```dart
// lib/src/core/notifications/notification_service.dart
abstract class NotificationService {
  Future<void> initialize();
  Future<void> scheduleDeadlineReminder({
    required String programmeId,
    required String programmeName,
    required DateTime deadline,
  });
  Future<void> cancel(String programmeId);
}
```
Each main_*.dart overrides `notificationServiceProvider` via Riverpod's `ProviderScope` overrides.

## Error handling
- Catch `PostgrestException` in the repository layer; throw domain exceptions.
- Never `try/catch` in a widget or provider build method.
- Sentry captures unhandled exceptions — wired in `main_*.dart` via `SentryFlutter.init`.

## Code style
- `const` constructors everywhere possible.
- One public widget per file; filename matches class name (snake_case ↔ PascalCase).
- Screen files: `*_screen.dart`. Reusable widgets: `*_card.dart`, `*_tile.dart`, etc.
- No logic in `build()`. Extract to a method or provider if it needs more than one expression.
- Private members prefixed `_`.
- Avoid `late` unless absolutely necessary; prefer nullable + null-check.
